EN: He exercised his power to reform the entire education system.

ZH: 行使权力要有责任感和公正评估。
EN: The exercise of power requires a sense of responsibility and fair assessment.

ZH: 他们必须行使条约中规定的权利和义务。
EN: They must exercise the rights and obligations stipulated in the treaty.

ZH: 这个组织行使着监督和管理职能。
EN: This organization exercises supervisory and managerial functions.

ZH: 行使决策的权力需要充分的信息和思考。
EN: Exercise of the power to make decisions requires adequate information and reflection.

ZH: 我们应该行使自己的公民权利来推动社会进步。
EN: We should exercise our citizen rights to promote social progress.

