EN: Teachers need to exercise authority to maintain classroom discipline.

ZH: 行使公正和公正的司法系统对社会至关重要。
EN: Exercising a fair and impartial judicial system is crucial to society.

ZH: 让我们行使自由言论的权利，表达我们的意见。
EN: Let us exercise our right to freedom of speech and express our opinions.
